{"tid":1106994,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[EA驚]《星球大戰 絕地: 組織殞落》","createTime":"2019-04-15T02:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T23:18:37.000Z","uid":33799,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a71f59857797ec76982d78480c8158bbf3cd5014","tid":1106994,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:34:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rg1WzkgJi98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRg1WzkgJi98&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=1d1a6270\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rg1WzkgJi98</a><br />\n<br />\n稍早在美國芝加哥舉行的「Star Wars Celebration」期間，Respawn Entertainment 正式公開《星際大戰 絕地：組織殞落》（Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order）首支宣傳片，預計 11 月 15 日開賣，全新主角凱爾克提斯正式亮相！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/TangBao/1904/14-swjedi08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FTangBao%2F1904%2F14-swjedi08.jpg&h=9d3a6832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲背景描述《星際大戰三部曲：西斯大帝的復仇》66 號密令肅清行動結束，玩家將於全新《星際大戰》星球「Bracca」遇見絕地組織僅存學徒（Padawan）「凱爾克提斯」（Cal Kestis），因為不小心展露原力，被迫亡命天涯，途中他必須遵守生存原則，包括不能相信任何人、接受過去，外加不要引人注目，要在帝國判官發現意圖重建絕地組織前，完成訓練。<br />\n<br />\n附帶一提，凱爾並不是一個人，除了他的神秘夥伴 Cere，還有一個機器人夥伴 BD-1（預告片有）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/TangBao/1904/14-swjedi02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FTangBao%2F1904%2F14-swjedi02.jpg&h=0cfa74fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本次出席活動的 Respawn 開發團隊透露，《星球大戰 絕地：組織殞落》為第三人稱動作冒險類型，採用 Unreal Engine 4 開發，僅有單人模式，沒有多人模式，也沒有微交易模式，全力專注劇情鋪陳，包括激烈的光劍戰鬥。</span><br />\n<br />\n標榜創新的光劍戰鬥系統，同時具備各式攻擊、格擋、閃避等豐富動作要素，外加原力技能，滿足玩家成為絕地武士的渴望，外加豐富的銀河系探索可能性。<br />\n<br />\n除令人懷念的《星際大戰》既有世界觀與相關要素，這次同時會導入《星際大戰》全新角色、地點、生物、機器人與敵軍。Lucasfilm Story Group 品牌系列內容與策略總監 Steve Blank 指出，聽聞 Respawn 向他們提出新作構思時，立即給予支持，一個單人且劇情導向的遊戲新作，正是他們同樣在尋求的目標。<br />\n<br />\n好撚興奮, 但係都係個句, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經被EA撚左好多次, NO PRE-ORDER</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b0cdd6fec36953cc25a0356fed4816dda1be83","tid":1106994,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"Respawn真係好撚怪<br />\n當年Titanfall純多人冇單人<br />\n而家呢隻就純單人冇多人<br />\n到底做乜9"},{"pid":"aef78a7155bd39ae74ef8c4c25b68027c82684d7","tid":1106994,"uid":58120,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"96b0cdd6fec36953cc25a0356fed4816dda1be83","tid":1106994,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"Respawn真係好撚怪<br />\n當年Titanfall純多人冇單人<br />\n而家呢隻就純單人冇多人<br />\n到底做乜9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"話你on9驚你嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084dc999f2c332f67f6c4effe8aae93652a0b694","tid":1106994,"uid":13543,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:12:29.000Z","msg":"好矛盾<br />\n驚佢整得柒<br />\n但又有D期待"},{"pid":"4540e73bf27defdc5d287e867b920d2949298d4a","tid":1106994,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"084dc999f2c332f67f6c4effe8aae93652a0b694","tid":1106994,"uid":13543,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:12:29.000Z","msg":"好矛盾<br />\n驚佢整得柒<br />\n但又有D期待"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:16:08.000Z","msg":"所以都係睇定啲先好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072505e1c22782a6012ac7fec8b4854bc60e9d88","tid":1106994,"uid":89857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:18:11.000Z","msg":"同anthem一樣鳩<br />\ntrailer整到好撚正<br />\n出到黎伏撚到仆街"},{"pid":"c1493683676c63363795a576e37247d215150373","tid":1106994,"uid":38821,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96b0cdd6fec36953cc25a0356fed4816dda1be83","tid":1106994,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"Respawn真係好撚怪<br />\n當年Titanfall純多人冇單人<br />\n而家呢隻就純單人冇多人<br />\n到底做乜9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:19:42.000Z","msg":"TF1個idea好似係將故事融入multiplay入面.<br />\n結果梗係fail, 當然係人都知佢係懶居多.<br />\n所以TF2咪比返個好正既單人模式.<br />\n<br />\n其實自從SW翻生後我就覺得佢好適合出一隻mass effect類型既單機驚.<br />\n呢隻我應該都會狗衝架喇.<br />\n雖然utube上EA 3 rules:<br />\n1. Don't pre-order<br />\n2. Remember the past<br />\n3. Don't trust EA"},{"pid":"49b2f3fd535bf772307117ef088230d109b85eea","tid":1106994,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:20:35.000Z","msg":"EA PreOrder 不了<br />\n等隻game出晒gameplay 片同hands on review 再算"},{"pid":"95da6e6b33c5f17b6730a85a552f307f44d5939a","tid":1106994,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"應該係十幾個鐘就爆機<br />\n又冇自由度嘅驚<br />\n所以ea先咁好人唔加loot box<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d15bd8a15862a10177a7991e30e34341e35ef6","tid":1106994,"uid":56261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"出返Jedi academy仲好"},{"pid":"f4ebe041305aab7f5430346235de8f4a1de5c4cb","tid":1106994,"uid":38821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95da6e6b33c5f17b6730a85a552f307f44d5939a","tid":1106994,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"應該係十幾個鐘就爆機<br />\n又冇自由度嘅驚<br />\n所以ea先咁好人唔加loot box<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"EA信唔過, <br />\n但Respawn呢幾年口碑算唔錯ge.<br />\n唯有希望唔好星戰先黎fuck up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{